<span id="freeTextContainer16324641542851646926">I haven&apos;t seen many plays performed so it&apos;s difficult for me to imagine how this intense &amp; potent little book would render onstage. I&apos;m pretty sure it&apos;d be amazing though. Extra rewarding for someone who&apos;s fascinated by musician&apos;s culture and the process of recording, as all the action takes place in a studio during a session.</span>
  <span id="freeText16324641542851646926" style="display:none">I haven't seen many plays performed so it's difficult for me to imagine how this intense &amp; potent little book would render onstage. I'm pretty sure it'd be amazing though. Extra rewarding for someone who's fascinated by musician's culture and the process of recording, as all the action takes place in a studio during a session.</span>
